text: Pai Yun-yiao (born 14 March 1969) is a Taiwanese taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in flyweight at the 1987 World Taekwondo Championships in Barcelona. She won a silver medal at the 1989 World Taekwondo Championships, after being defeated by Won Sun-jin in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
